West Hammers defender Carl Jenkinson says Jack Grealish should follow his heart when choosing between Ireland or England . 
  The Aston Villa midfielder is on loan from Arsenal until the end of the season . 
  Jenkinson chose England in 2012 despite playing for Finland at youth level . 
  The West Ham defender played for Ireland at Under 21 level . 
  He says he was in the same situation when he chose England over Finland in 2012 . 
  The winger can still play for the England senior side . 
 